<section>
<h2>Formats</h2>
<h3>vCard</h3>
<pre><code contenteditable>BEGIN:VCARD
VERSION:2.1
N:Last;First
FN:Full name
ORG:Organization
TITLE:Occupation title
TEL;WORK;VOICE:(604) 123-4567
TEL;HOME;VOICE:(778) 123-4567
ADR;WORK:;;100 Waters Edge;Vancouver;BC;V7V7V7;Canada
LABEL;WORK;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:100 Waters Edge=0D=Vancouver, BC V7V7V7=0D=0ACanada
ADR;HOME:;;42 Plantation St.;Vancouver;BC;V7V7V7;Canada
LABEL;HOME;ENCODING=QUOTED-PRINTABLE:42 Plantation St.=0D=Vancouver, BC V7V7V7=0D=0ACanada
EMAIL;PREF;INTERNET:email@address.ca
REV:20080424T195243Z
END:VCARD</code></pre>
<p><small><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vcard">vCard format standard (wikipedia)</a></small></p>
</section>

<section>
<h2>Formats</h2>
<h3>meCard</h3>
<pre><code contenteditable>MECARD:
N:Last,First;
NOTE:Occupation title;
TEL:16041234567;
EMAIL:email@address.ca;
URL:http://www.website.com;;</code></pre>
<p><small><a href="https://www.nttdocomo.co.jp/english/service/developer/make/content/barcode/function/application/addressbook/index.html">meCard format standard</a></small></p>
</section>

